---

This project includes components and inspiration from:

- Netmaker (https://github.com/gravitl/netmaker) - Apache 2.0 License
- Mosquitto MQTT Broker - Eclipse Public License
- Nginx - 2-clause BSD License
- OpenVSwitch - Apache 2.0 License

This software is based on real-world deployment experience from the GhostBridge
project and extensive troubleshooting to address common installation issues.

DISCLAIMER: This is a community-maintained installation suite. While thoroughly
tested based on real-world deployments, please review configurations and 
security settings for your specific environment before production deployment.

The installation scripts are designed to automate the setup process and address
common pitfalls encountered during Netmaker installations, particularly:
- MQTT broker connection failures
- Nginx stream module configuration issues  
- Network configuration problems in containerized environments
- SSL certificate setup and management

For support and contributions, please visit:
https://github.com/your-username/netmaker_non-containerized_GO_stack